casebody.data:
No.-. Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of St. Louis, Kansas City & Colorado Railroad Company. Submitted January 15, 1917. Decided January 22, 1917.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of prohibition and mandamus denied, without prejudice in any respect to relief on appeal or otherwise on the merits. Mr. Thomas P. Littlepage, Mr. Paul E. Walker, Mr. James C. Jones, Mr. Lon O. Hocker, Mr. Frank D. Sullivan and Mr. Marcus L. Bell for the petitioner.
